The paper deals with representation learning using video data, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of self-supervised learning is also a key aspect of the paper, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also utilizes multiple modalities (RGB and optical flow), which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM). The paper's focus on exploiting cross-modal information could also be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
